The **Radial Column** series, also known as the *Circular Column chart*, displays data using rectangular columns that are positioned along a polar axis. This chart type is similar to the [Nightingale Chart](./charts-nightingale-series).

## Grouped Radial Column

To create a basic Radial Column chart, use a data array where each item has one category value (for the angle axis) and one numeric value (for the radius axis).

A minimal Radial Column series configuration will look like:

```js
series: [
    {
        type: 'radial-column',
        angleKey: 'product',
        radiusKey: 'sales',
    },
],
```

